snippet.title: TRANSFORMERS: REACTIVATE Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
The gravest threat to humanity has arrived. And it’s already won. 
 
Earth is no longer ours; it belongs to them. 
  
Fight back against the Legion in TRANSFORMERS: REACTIVATE, the new 1-4 player online action game from Splash Damage.  
 
Coming to PC and consoles, sign up for updates at PlayTFR.com 
  
Follow TRANSFORMERS: REACTIVATE - 
https://www.Youtube.com/PlayTFR 
https://www.twitter.com/PlayTFR 
https://www.facebook.com/PlayTFR 
https://www.instagram.com/PlayTFR 
https://www.tiktok.com/@PlayTFR 
  
Press and content creators can register for updates at https://press.splashdamage.com  
  
Follow Splash Damage: 
https://www.Youtube.com/SplashDamage 
https://www.twitter.com/SplashDamage 
https://www.facebook.com/SplashDamage 
https://www.instagram.com/Splash_Damage 
https://www.linkedin.com/company/splash-damage/   
  
#Transformers #Hasbro #TheGameAwards #Gaming #VideoGames #playtfr

Subscribe to the Hasbro Pulse YouTube Channel: https://bit.ly/3FzcXKW

Website - http://bit.ly/3hrkSC2

Hasbro Pulse is a place where fans come first.

As fans ourselves, we have an idea of what you – our fans – want. Hasbro Pulse is where you’ll find some of the best product offerings and experiences from the brands you love, a glimpse at more behind-the-scenes material and insider details that you can’t get anywhere else.

We made Hasbro Pulse with you, the fans, in mind. We hope you’ll make it your first stop when you’re looking for insider info about your favorite Hasbro brands.
